---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Pricing - R.O. bot" description="R.O. bot pricing for automotive service departments. See how voice-first AI can help your techs find more work, sell more work, and get paid for more work." canonicalPath="/pricing">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy pt-28 pb-16 md:pt-36 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Simple Pricing That Pays for Itself
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        R.O. bot is priced per store, per month. Most shops see ROI within the first few weeks from time savings and improved warranty approval rates alone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-12 text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-teal font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Per Store, Per Month</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-4">
          Let's Find the Right Plan for Your Team
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Pricing depends on your store count and which R.O. bot tools your team needs. Book a 15-minute call and we'll walk you through the options.
        </p>
        <a href="/book-demo" class="inline-block bg-teal hover:bg-teal-dark text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg transition-colors">
          Get a Custom Quote
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- What's included -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10">What Every Plan Includes</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Voice-First Documentation</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Techs speak, R.O. bot writes. Complete 3Cs stories generated from voice notes, graded against OEM standards.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">AI-Guided Video Inspections</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            On-screen teleprompter guides techs through professional inspection videos that customers understand and approve.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-navy mb-2">Voice-First Multi-Point Inspections</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Techs call out findings as they work. Higher completion rates, more issues discovered, zero clipboard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Also included list -->
      <div class="bg-navy rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Also Included</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Unlimited technicians per store</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Works on any phone or tablet</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">No DMS integration required</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Up and running in 10 minutes</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Story grading and quality scoring</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white/80">Dedicated onboarding support</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROI framing -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-10">The Math Is Simple</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal mb-2">30+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Minutes saved per tech, per day on documentation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal mb-2">12%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Industry-average warranty denial rate that better stories can reduce</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-teal mb-2">10 min</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">From download to first voice-generated repair story</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        One recovered warranty claim or one extra hour of wrench time per tech per week typically covers the cost of R.O. bot many times over.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-navy text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">See How the Numbers Work for Your Shop</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-8">Book a 15-minute demo and we'll walk through the pricing and ROI for your specific situation.</p>
      <a href="/book-demo" class="inline-block bg-teal hover:bg-teal-dark text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg transition-colors">
        Book Your Demo
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
